sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client Application
    participant P as Panorama
    participant FW1 as Firewall 1
    participant FW2 as Firewall 2
    participant FW3 as Firewall 3
    note over P: Configured as<br/>Redistribution Agent
    C ->>+ P: XML API Request:<br/>Register new IP tag
    P ->> P: Process IP tag<br/>registration
    P -->>- C: Response: Success

    rect rgb(200, 220, 255)
        note over P, FW3: Tag Distribution Phase
        par Distribution to Firewalls
            P ->> FW1: Push IP tag update
            P ->> FW2: Push IP tag update
            P ->> FW3: Push IP tag update
        end
    end

    par Acknowledgment
        FW1 -->> P: Confirm tag received
        FW2 -->> P: Confirm tag received
        FW3 -->> P: Confirm tag received
    end

    note over FW1, FW3: Firewalls update their<br/>local DAG memberships